xwikidoc.content:
Wiki macros implementation of the [[LiveValidation javascript framework>>http://livevalidation.com/documentation]] to be used with validation specified in XWiki classes.

== Macros ==

|扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱}|Provides client-side live validation of a single XObject based on the validation expressions and messages defined in its XClass.
|扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱悯篝镯}|Validates a XObject property value using a custom remote XWiki document that should returns "true" when valid or "false" when not valid, based on the field value and the property reference.
|扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱彭衢}|Validates that XObject property value is a valid email address.
|扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱骑蝽狒}|Validates that XObject property value against a regular expression.
|扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱序弩孱沐}|Validates that XObject property value is present (ie. not null, undefined, or an empty string).

== Usage ==

{{code language='none'}}
{{livevalidation form='inline' object='objectReference' /}}

{{livevalidationPresence form='formId' property='propertyReference' failureMessage='Non empty value required.' /}}

{{livevalidationFormat form='formId' property='propertyReference' pattern='[A-Z]+' failureMessage='Only uppercase characters allowed.' /}}

{{livevalidationEmail form='formId' property='propertyReference' failureMessage='Email format invalid.' /}}

{{livevalidationCustom form='formId' property='propertyReference' against='validationDocumentReference' failureMessage='Invalid value.'/}}
{{/code}}

{{info}}
Either leave an empty space between macro calls to avoid inlining or put them all next to each other for inlining, both will work properly.
{{/info}}

== 扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱} ==
{{code language="none"}}
{{livevalidation form='formId' object='objectReference' /}}
{{/code}}
|= Param |= Description
| form | Unique ID of the form html element that will be validated before submission.
| object | [[Object reference>>http://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/Model+Module#HObjectReferences]] of the XObject to be validated.

== 扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱序弩孱沐} ==
{{code language="none"}}
{{livevalidationPresence form='formId' property='propertyReference' failureMessage='Non empty value required.' /}}
{{/code}}
|= Param |= Description
| form | Unique ID of the form html element that contains the validated field.
| property | [[Property reference>>http://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/Model+Module#HPropertyReferences]] of the field to be validated.
| failureMessage | Message to be used upon validation failure.

== 扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱骑蝽狒} ==
{{code language="none"}}
{{livevalidationFormat form="formId" property="propertyReference" pattern="/regex/" failureMessage="A message to display when validation fail" /}}
{{/code}}
|= Param |= Description
| form | Unique ID of the form html element that contains the validated field.
| property | [[Property reference>>http://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/Model+Module#HPropertyReferences]] of the field to be validated.
| pattern | A regular expression pattern in Javascript syntax.
| failureMessage | Message to be used upon validation failure.

== 扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱彭衢} ==
{{code language="none"}}
{{livevalidationEmail form="formId" property="propertyReference" failureMessage="A message to display when validation fail" /}}
{{/code}}
|= Param |= Description
| form | Unique ID of the form html element that contains the validated field.
| property | [[Property reference>>http://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/Model+Module#HPropertyReferences]] of the field to be validated.
| failureMessage | Message to be used upon validation failure.

== 扉鲥鲠扉溽糸镱悯篝镯} ==
{{code language="none"}}
{{livevalidationCustom form="formId" property="propertyReference" against="validationDocumentReference" args="an=additional&query=string" failureMessage="A message to display when false is returned" /}}
{{/code}}
|= Param |= Description
| form | Unique ID of the form html element that contains the validated field.
| property | [[Property reference>>http://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/Model+Module#HPropertyReferences]] of the field to be validated.
| against | Document reference of the document that will be AJAX requested to settle the validation.
| args | Additional QueryString passed over to the requested document with the property reference and the field value.
| failureMessage | Message to be used upon validation failure.

== Examples ==

Add the following lines to ##MyApp.MyAppSheet##:

{{code language='none'}}
{{livevalidation form='inline' object='MyApp.MyAppClass[0]' /}}

{{livevalidationPresence form='inline' property='MyApp.MyAppClass[0].myprop' failureMessage='myprop cannot be empty.' /}}

{{livevalidationFormat form='inline' property='MyApp.MyAppClass[0].myprop' pattern='/^[A-Z]*$/' failureMessage='myprop must contain only uppercase characters.' /}}

{{livevalidationEmail form='inline' property='MyApp.MyAppClass[0].myprop' failureMessage='Email format is invalid.' /}}

{{livevalidationCustom form='inline' property='MyApp.MyAppClass[0].myprop' against='Code.IsUniqueValidator' failureMessage='myprop is required to be unique.' /}}
{{/code}}
